Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平胡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:05.89,Chapter,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HB1FCF9&}{\1c&HBB6066&}啊啊 喜欢是动摇人心之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是天界服务技术第一的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也敌不过她的好运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我把机车推出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多好去完成另一项任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的另一项任务…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也闹得够呛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近天天都那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些话要对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 你对蓓儿丹蒂好好地说过喜欢她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么要说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这次任务中 一直观察着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你实在太缺乏积极性了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能就这样放着你们不管 背负败名回到天界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈什么哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我该…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 你对女性要更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思 马上就去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为你能逃得掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要让你说出“喜欢”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这里是WHIRLWIND
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 今天照常营业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉原的消声器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可以免费送货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“说过喜欢她吗”…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是喜欢 可是真要说出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会传染吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来喝下午茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子果然是被说“喜欢”会比较开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要对我告白我会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来如此 森里难道认为即使不说出来对方也能理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子啊 一直都很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在追寻着确认的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"喜欢"这句话 比起上百个礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能让女孩子感动和安心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的话 就赶紧行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里他有件很重要的事要对蓓儿说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢森里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 森里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下人才交流中心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是礼拜天 应该不开门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没种的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来再好好教训你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是没种呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来要下猛药了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗 要说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“喜欢”吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有多少年没听到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“喜欢”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随处可见的简单词汇 却包含着重要含义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街上洋溢着“喜欢”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢 喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对她 对最爱的她传达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好犹豫的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 现在应该能说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\ann8}（最喜欢猫实市了！）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是没说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别做了 不适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 欢迎回来 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 怕什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不会把你吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特·训
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特训？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 把我当成蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 对我说“喜欢” 来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种话 就这么随随便便说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会这么想 是因为心里有一个限制器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你知道“喜欢”这个词包含着无穷的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要把这个限制器给破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的那份心意 就能够随时加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（限制器吗…真会说话）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 打开心灵的加速器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,语言如旋律 思念如歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更用心一些 摇动对方的心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的旋律能抵达 我的心也会动摇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 不过还是不够
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再强烈一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（对 我想要自己亲口传达）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（蓓儿丹蒂…想对你传达）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动摇了 但是还要更…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对她传达的话 这种程度还远远不够！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一　洗澡水放好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵　这下有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是… 等等！这是误会！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你遇到麻烦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有很深的烦恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德 你又偷听了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是爱之丘比特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要告诉我 随时都能为你排忧解难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想说“喜欢”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je t'aime（法语）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你（汉语）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ich liebe dich（德语）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chan rak khun（泰语）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ti amo（意大利语）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Te amo（西班牙语）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,****
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(韩语)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Я любю тебя（俄语）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪儿学来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单单这样练习是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是发自内心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 对脸皮薄的萤一来说很难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很开心啊 兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 我是在担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我特别为你准备了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是吃了这东西 不知道会变成什么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这样说我的药也太失礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你自己吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让我们看看这药的效果是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀…兀儿德？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩欧丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:15:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩欧丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的……还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这药的效果不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 兀儿德老是捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩欧丝你不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说了 看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 为什么那么在意我的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是因为我是女神了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你幸福是我的使命 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是因为萤一的周围散发着一种“无法放任不管光环”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“无法放任不管光环”？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 又开始散发了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…让人放心不下的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这么乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:17:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么啊 你的阴谋已经被我看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才被你摆了一道 到底那是什么药？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么危险的东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“喜欢”不是光用语言就能传达的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是对于像萤一这样的男孩子来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我制作了这个仅仅增幅"喜欢"\N这个词的力量的特殊增幅药
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 听上去很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…刚才…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我只是稍微有点吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是某种练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:18:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…稍微有点羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羡慕？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 无论何时听到“喜欢”这个词 总是会开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是萤一所说的话…那就更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（女孩子啊 一直都很不安）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了要对你说喜欢而…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（喜欢喜欢喜欢…）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？说了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂！你怎么了？蓓儿丹蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太…太…太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太秽亵了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想对我的姐姐做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给出合理解释不会放过你哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是误会 我什么都没做！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是为了说出“喜欢”…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（喜欢喜欢喜欢…）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪 为什么效力那么强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为接受了我的特训嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德 佩欧丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是你们搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我可什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不是还说了“多亏了我的特训”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 还不是因为你那奇怪的药
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我的药奇怪是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩欧丝的特训才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打架我奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去可怎么办 想杀了我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：想杀了我吗？（ころすきか？）包含了关键词すき
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（喜欢！喜欢！喜欢！…）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不好意思…有谁来帮我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32\pos(685,55)}{\clip(685,23,718,55)\t(\clip(685,55,718,279))}果\N然\N是\N危\N险\N的\N药
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32\pos(685,55)}果\N然\N是\N危\N险\N的\N药
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 把我当实验品有啥开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 刚才我都六神无主了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉…成百上千的萤一的感情涌入心中…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然吓了一跳 但是非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“喜欢”这个词 真是太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（佩欧丝就是为了这个…）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 刚才没有好好地向你传达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…刚才晕了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你再说一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.26,0:21:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我会好好听着的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是最喜欢的人所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好谢谢佩欧丝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她提供了这个契机 让我有了向你传达这份心意的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：说出来的契机（出すきっかけ）包含了すき…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样叫我怎么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次…下次一定会好好听着的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.77,0:22:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是让人放心不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 真是太没出息了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能让你对姐姐说“喜欢”呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森里有没有说出来啊
